v-model.description: Use v-model to bind a boolean variable to open or close the picker
v-model.description_zh: 通过v-model双向绑定一个值为布尔值的变量，来打开或者收起picker

params.description: The parameters that need to be displayed are valid when mode=region or mode=time is shown above
params.description_zh: 需要显示的参数，见上方说明，mode=region或mode=time时有效

mode.description: Mode selection, region-region mode, time-time mode, selector-single-column mode, multiSelector-multi-column mode
mode.description_zh: 模式选择，region-地区模式，time-时间模式，selector-单列模式，multiSelector-多列模式

start-year.description: Optional start year, valid at mode=time
start-year.description_zh: 可选的开始年份，mode=time时有效

end-year.description: Optional end year, valid at mode=time
end-year.description_zh: 可选的结束年份，mode=time时有效

safe-area-inset-bottom.description: Whether to enable the bottom safe zone adaptation
safe-area-inset-bottom.description_zh: 是否开启底部安全区适配

cancel-color.description: The color of the cancel button

confirm-color.description: Confirm the color of the button

default-time.description: By default, mode=time is selected, and the value must be assigned to the onReady lifecycle, as described in the top
default-time.description_zh: 默认选中的时间，mode=time时有效，需在onReady生命周期赋值，见顶部说明

default-region.description: The default selected region, in Chinese, mode=region, needs to be assigned in the onReady lifecycle, see the top description
default-region.description_zh: 默认选中的地区，中文形式，mode=region时有效，需在onReady生命周期赋值，见顶部说明

area-code.description: By default, the selected region is numbered and valid when mode=region is selected
area-code.description_zh: 默认选中的地区，编号形式，mode=region时有效

default-selector.description: array, where each term indicates the number of range equivalents selected (the subscript starts at 0), as explained above
default-selector.description_zh: 数组形式，其中每一项表示选择了range对应项中的第几个(下标从0开始)，见上方说明

mask-close-able.description: Whether or not to allow Picker to be turned off by clicking on the mask
mask-close-able.description_zh: 是否允许通过点击遮罩关闭Picker

show-time-tag.description: In time mode, whether to display the following year, month and day Chinese prompts
show-time-tag.description_zh: 时间模式时，是否显示后面的年月日中文提示

z-index.description: The value of the z-index when it pops up

range.description: Custom selected data is valid when mode=selector or mode=multiSelector
range.description_zh: 自定义选择的数据，mode=selector或mode=multiSelector时有效

range-key.description: When the element of the range parameter is an object, specify the value of the key in the object to be displayed as a selector, as described above
range-key.description_zh: 当range参数的元素为对象时，指定Object中的哪个key的值作为选择器显示内容，见上方说明

title.description: The title in the middle of the top

confirm-text.description: Confirm the text of the button

cancel-text.description: The text of the cancel button
